<div id="review_2272910548" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2272910548" />
    <a title="Hannah Greendale" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/43377498-hannah-greendale"><img alt="Hannah Greendale" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1466436186p2/43377498.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2272910548?book_show_action=true">Jan 30, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Hannah Greendale" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Hannah Greendale" href="/user/show/43377498-hannah-greendale">Hannah Greendale</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audiobook " href="/book/show/37555264-the-professor-and-the-madman">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/43377498-hannah-greendale?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/43377498-hannah-greendale?shelf=history">history</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/43377498-hannah-greendale?shelf=adult">adult</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/43377498-hannah-greendale?shelf=biography">biography</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/43377498-hannah-greendale?shelf=audiobook">audiobook</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2272910548" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4817440265874803482"><a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KlYG1hggK8c' rel='nofollow noopener'>Click here</a> to watch a video review of this book on my channel, <i>From Beginning to Bookend</i>.<br/><br/><a href='https://imgur.com/JOQrpqU' rel='nofollow noopener'>
  <img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1517418713i/24975476._SX540_.jpg' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/>
</a><br/><br/>Eloquent writing and the talented vocal work of narrator Simon Jones make this brief account of one of the greatest known editors of the OED and his longtime collaborator (a man who conducted his research from the confines of an asylum) a fascinating read/listen. <br/></span>
  <span id="freeText4817440265874803482" style="display:none"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KlYG1hggK8c" rel="nofollow noopener">Click here</a> to watch a video review of this book on my channel, <i>From Beginning to Bookend</i>.<br><br><a href="https://imgur.com/JOQrpqU" rel="nofollow noopener">
  <img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1517418713i/24975476._SX540_.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg">
</a><br><br>Eloquent writing and the talented vocal work of narrator Simon Jones make this brief account of one of the greatest known editors of the OED and his longtime collaborator (a man who conducted his research from the confines of an asylum) a fascinating read/listen. <br></span>
  <a data-text-id="4817440265874803482" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


