r into the eternally popular My Fair Lady (where Higgins was played, in the film, by the similarly rude and pig-headed actor Rex Harrison).</i><br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1425044300i/13835026._SY540_.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"> Frederick Furnivall<br></span>
